Package humandeque

package humandeque
Represents a collection of humans and provides common manipulations over it. The HumanDeque collection represents the target collection of the project and contains instances of Human objects. The CollectionManager class serves as an abstract base class for all managers and provides access to the HumanDeque collection instance and common manipulations over it. The LocalManager class is designed for local manipulations and can be used on both the client and server side.
